uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.collection

Interface SelfStreamDecorator<T,S extends SelfStreamDecorator<T,S>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the elements of the stream
    S - the final implementing class
    All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, BaseStream<T,Stream<T>>, Copyable<S>, Self<S>, Stream<T>

    public interface SelfStreamDecorator<T,S extends SelfStreamDecorator<T,S>>
extends Stream<T>, Self<S>
    A decorator for a Stream which wraps intermediate and terminal operations such that they can be easily extended.
